lqs / listquest               Lists all quests

   Format:
      ;lqs                    Lists all quests
      ;lqs <switch>           Lists all quests in a particular order
      ;lqs <name>             Lists information about the quest <name>

   Notes:
      Axmud is able to store information about the current world's quests. This
         command lists all the quests stored in the current world profile.
      If specified, <switch> can be any of the following:
         -q   - lists quests in order of quest points
         -x   - lists quests in order of XP
         -c   - lists quests in order of cash

   User commands:
      lqs / listqs / listquest
